videos.headline: Brandon Clarke rocks the rim with powerful jam

videos.description: Kyle Anderson tosses up the lob over a defender to Ja Morant, who slams it down with two hands to cap the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyle Anderson lobs to Ja Morant for the nice flush) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyle Anderson lobs to Ja Morant for the nice flush

videos.description: De'Anthony Melton drives to the basket and elevates to flush a dunk down over the contest of Karl-Anthony Towns

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (De'Anthony Melton throws down on KAT) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: De'Anthony Melton throws down on KAT

videos.description: Ja Morant uses a nice move to fake out Karl-Anthony Towns then sinks a sweet fadeaway jumper from midrange.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ja Morant drains fadeaway after faking out KAT with 360 spin) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ja Morant drains fadeaway after faking out KAT with 360 spin

videos.description: Karl-Anthony Towns races to grab the rebound and contorts his body to twist in a layup to beat the buzzer at the end of the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KAT makes sweet twisting shot to beat the buzzer) 2021/11/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: KAT makes sweet twisting shot to beat the buzzer

videos.description: Jaden McDaniels gets the nice pass from D'Angelo Russell and elevates to power down a dunk in the face of Ja Morant.

videos.headline: Jaden McDaniels throws down on Ja Morant

videos.description: Ja Morant beats his defender and takes flight to flush down a two-handed slam to tie the game  at 108-108 late in the fourth quarter.
